---
const whatsapp = "553298408646";
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-300 py-10 mt-16">
	<div class="container mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 px-6">
		<div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-start gap-3">
			<img src="/images/logo-tipo-div-comp-footer.png" alt="Logo DivComp" class="h-14 w-auto mb-1" loading="lazy" />
			<span class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base text-center md:text-left max-w-xs">
        Manutenção, redes e servidores.<br />
        Atendimento humanizado e confiança para empresas e residências em Divinésia/MG e região.
      </span>
		</div>
		<nav class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-1 md:gap-5 items-center mt-4 md:mt-0">
			<a href="/" class="hover:text-green-400 transition">Início</a>
			<a href="/servicos" class="hover:text-green-400 transition">Serviços</a>
			<a href="/sobre" class="hover:text-green-400 transition">Sobre</a>
			<a href="/faq" class="hover:text-green-400 transition">Dúvidas</a>
			<a href="/contato" class="hover:text-green-400 transition">Contato</a>
		</nav>
		<div class="flex flex-col items-center md:items-end gap-2">
			<div class="flex gap-4 items-center">
				<a href={`https://wa.me/${whatsapp}`} target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-green-400 hover:text-green-500 transition">
					<span class="icon-[ic--baseline-whatsapp] w-6 h-6"></span>
					WhatsApp
				</a>
				<a href="mailto:contato@divcomp.com.br" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-300 hover:text-yellow-300 transition">
					<span class="icon-[ic--baseline-email] w-6 h-6"></span>
					Email
				</a>
			</div>
			<span class="text-gray-400 text-xs">Divinésia/MG • Segunda a sábado, das 8h às 18h</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-green-800/10 text-center text-xs text-gray-500 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-2 px-6">
    <span>
      &copy; {year} DivComp Informática. Todos os direitos reservados.
    </span>
		<span>
      Desenvolvido por <span class="font-semibold text-green-400">Raimundo C Ferreira</span> — <span class="text-green-500 font-semibold">Sábio System Tecnologia</span>
    </span>
	</div>
</footer>
